WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:03.830
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries <i>:</i>

00:04.003 --> 00:05.995
- You must be Elena.
- How do we look alike?

00:06.172 --> 00:08.697
Petrova doppelganger,
the key to breaking the curse.

00:08.875 --> 00:09.899
Sun and Moon curse?

00:10.143 --> 00:14.136
Vampires and werewolves used to roam
freely until a shaman put a curse on them.

00:14.347 --> 00:16.372
- Klaus is the real deal.
- First generation.

00:16.549 --> 00:19.575
The oldest vampire in the history of time
is coming after me?

00:21.054 --> 00:24.046
- Katerina, I have missed you.
- Klaus.

00:24.290 --> 00:26.850
Klaus is in Alaric's body.
He's possessing it.

00:27.060 --> 00:29.688
Now, while I'm gone,
you stay here, Katerina.

00:31.931 --> 00:33.899
- Elijah.
- One of the Originals. A legend.

00:34.534 --> 00:35.762
- Uhn!
- So that's it.

00:35.935 --> 00:38.165
As long as we keep
the dagger in, he stays dead?

00:38.371 --> 00:40.498
Elijah had no weapon to kill Klaus.

00:40.707 --> 00:44.473
But he believed if a witch could channel
enough power, they wouldn't need one.

00:44.644 --> 00:47.044
Says if you use too much powers,
it'll kill you.

00:47.247 --> 00:49.613
Bonnie won't die for me.
I won't let that happen.

00:49.783 --> 00:52.775
- She's the only one who can do it.
- We'll find another way.

